<br>
Wingblade is dropped by the Spiroc Lord, on the 5th island (depending on how you count 'em)<br>
<br>
You don't need a map for PoA, it's just 9 small floating islands. You kill mobs on each island and they drop a key quest piece. You kill the boss mob of the island and the quest dude spawns, little angry assling feller called Sirran the Lunatic (he doubles for 2K, don't piss him off) hang in the key quest piece, get the key to the next island.<br>
<br>
Rinse and repeat until on the Spiroc island. Look at alla's for information on PoA, they have links to some good guides <p>--
